	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[1.66]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I have compared all of the stats for all the races that can become a druid.&nbsp;&nbsp;Humans are the best.  They are stronger and have more life (good for soloing when you run out of mana). Although there agility is definatlly lacking.  there wis is only 5 points behind a woodelf or halfling.  So if you can't stand the annoying town of kelethin and don't want to look like a gay guy in his mid 40s with a growth problem.  Be a human and be proud!<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
